description:
APPLICABILITY
Applicable to general wholesale power service for industrial, commercial and
agricultural purposes, subject to special conditions hereinafter stated.
Applicable to standby or breakdown service where the entire electric power
requirements on the customer's premises are not regularly supplied by the District.
A charge of $0.26 per kilovar of reactive demand as measured by the incoming kilovar demand meter for each kilovar in excess of .60 times the kilowatt demand measured and supplied by the District.
name: SCHEDULE A-2 GENERAL WHOLESALE POWER SERVICE
